UMB : Designated Professional Services Exclusion ZC3676
Description

PLP 4485

Line of business : Umbrella

Coverage Number : ZC 3676

Type : Exclusion

Exclusion Name : Designated Professional Services

Business Objective :

To implement a new exclusion coverage under UMB to restrict claims arising from designated professional services as defined by exclusion ZC 3676.

Requirements :

R1) UI requirements : Add a new exclusion:

As a policy center user, I want a new exclusion under Umbrella ZC 3676 Exclusion - Designated Professional Services.
So that I can select the exclusion and add it on transaction.

Exclusion should appear on :

New business
Renewal
Policy change
Rewrite

Exclusion Type : Optional

R2) Form Attachment

Upon selection of the exclusion ZC 3676 attach the document automatically to the final policy documents based on the language selected.

Include proper versioning and form edition date.

R3) Coverage Terms:

Add a schedule box for ZC 3676 which will display only when user selects ZC 3676 on UI were user can click on "Add" to add a schedule row.

A free form text field available for user to enter the "Designated professional services excluded".( upto 250 characters)

User may enter as many rows as required.

R4) Validation Rules :

When user selects ZC 3676 on UI and does not enter a schedule then an OOTB error message to trigger.

R5) Effective date of the new exclusion :

The new exclusion to be available for selection only on the policies/ renewals starting from August release live date.